headline: Prediction: 2 Stocks Will Be Worth More Than Palantir Technologies in 2026
summary: Palantir is currently worth $269 billion, but certain Wall Street analysts think Intuitive Surgical and ServiceNow can top that figure in 2026.  ServiceNow is a leader in IT service management and IT operations software, and recently released AI products are driving revenue growth.  Intuitive Surgical is a technology leader in robotics-assisted surgical systems, and it recently won new approvals from the FDA.
